Faoi Gheall ag Eirinn

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Lynette Fay, published by BBC in 2016 - Irish narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/a/a0/Faoi-Gheall-ag-Eirinn-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
English title: Pledged to Ireland.

Tells the compelling stories of three Ulster women: Tyrone-born writer Alice Milligan, and Belfast Cumann na mBan activists Elizabeth and Nell Corr, who made significant contributions to Irish political and cultural life in the lead up to and during the Easter Rising in 1916.
